originalText.text: Dr. Zhao has been my PCP for ten years, and has always provided me with high quality, individualized care. She has a wonderful bedside manner and I never feel rushed in our appointments. I am a health care provider and have referred many patients to her over the years, and their feedback has  been very positive. Notably, she helped one of them receive a definitive diagnosis for a rare disorder that none of his other doctors had caught. I completely trust her, and everyone she has referred me to has also been professional and competent.
